.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, hedgehog, rabbit, rat, snake, guinea-pig
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, engineer, journalist, manager, musician, photographer
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, scooter, snowmobile, taxi, trike, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the accountant##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is the journalist##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the photographer##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the person driving the roller is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
13. the owner of the cat is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the person driving the van is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Pet    | cat     | rat   | snake        | hamster   | hedgehog     | rabbit     | guinea-pig    |
| Job         | analyst    | journalist | accountant | manager | photographer | musician | engineer |
| Transport   | helicopter | taxi       | roller     | scooter | snowmobile   | trike    | van      |

