 9. the owner of the pony is the person playing canasta##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
11. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing domino##1
15. the person playing canasta is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
