The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, gardening, photography, skydiving, traveling, writing
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, january, march, september, may, august, april
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's hobby is writing##2
